  "prompt": "If I am talking on whatsapp call to someone and another person calls me on my whatsapp. what status will he get. will it show busy?",
  "response": "When you are on a WhatsApp call and another person tries to call you on WhatsApp, the caller will typically see a \"ringing\" status or \"calling.\" However, they will receive a notification indicating that you are currently on another call. They will not get a \"busy\" signal as it happens with traditional phone lines. Instead, they might receive a message stating that you are unavailable or busy. Once your current call is ended, they can try calling you again.",
